data.name: Nature_1_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the bold type!

data.name: Nature_1_2
data.value: You're so brave, and you never back down from anything! And you're also gutsy and brash in a way that others aren't!

data.name: Nature_1_3
data.value: You're not shy about asking to take home all the leftovers at restaurants, right?

data.name: Nature_1_4
data.value: If someone's treating you to dinner, you have no problem with ordering lots of good stuff!

data.name: Nature_1_5
data.value: And you aren't fazed by doing things that most others would think twice about doing.

data.name: Nature_1_6
data.value: Perhaps you don't even notice when others are upset with you!

data.name: Nature_1_7
data.value: You know, you have the potential to become a truly great person...because you'll be the last one standing!

data.name: Nature_1_8
data.value: So, a bold type like you...

data.name: Nature_2_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the brave type!

data.name: Nature_2_2
data.value: You don't know the meaning of fear! You're not afraid to keep moving forward in the face of danger.

data.name: Nature_2_3
data.value: You also have a strong sense of justice and can't turn a blind eye to someone in trouble.

data.name: Nature_2_4
data.value: But you sometimes push your own personal sense of justice a little too hard. Be careful that you don't get too pushy!

data.name: Nature_2_5
data.value: So, a brave type like you...

data.name: Nature_3_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the calm type!

data.name: Nature_3_2
data.value: You're very compassionate and considerate, and you put friends ahead of yourself.

data.name: Nature_3_3
data.value: You're so generous and kindhearted that you can laugh, forgive, and forget when your friends make mistakes.

data.name: Nature_3_4
data.value: But be aware that your compassion can sometimes get the best of you, putting you too far behind everyone else!

data.name: Nature_3_5
data.value: So, a calm type like you...

data.name: Nature_4_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the docile type! You're quite sensitive to others!

data.name: Nature_4_2
data.value: You listen attentively and respectfully, and you're quick to pick up on things.

data.name: Nature_4_3
data.value: Because you're so good at listening, do you find that your friends tell you their problems and concerns often?

data.name: Nature_4_4
data.value: Perhaps people laugh at you sometimes for being so earnest and not recognizing jokes for what they are.

data.name: Nature_4_5
data.value: But you're honestly surprised and bashful about this aspect of yourself...And then honestly laugh about it!

data.name: Nature_4_6
data.value: So, a docile, sensitive type like you...

data.name: Nature_5_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the hardy type! You're so determined!

data.name: Nature_5_2
data.value: You don't whine or feel sorry for yourself, and you never need help with anything. You also have a strong sense of responsibility.

data.name: Nature_5_3
data.value: You work toward your goals steadily and never require attention along the way.

data.name: Nature_5_4
data.value: Your resilient spirit is the only thing you need to guide you toward your goals.

data.name: Nature_5_5
data.value: But be careful! You risk wearing yourself out if you work too long all on your own!

data.name: Nature_5_6
data.value: You should recognize that sometimes you need help from friends.

data.name: Nature_5_7
data.value: So, a hardy, determined type like you...

data.name: Nature_6_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the hasty type!

data.name: Nature_6_2
data.value: You talk quickly! You eat quickly! You walk quickly!

data.name: Nature_6_3
data.value: People often see you as a hard worker because you're always moving around so fast!

data.name: Nature_6_4
data.value: But be careful! If you always rush so fast, you may make mistakes more often than others do. And what a waste that would be!

data.name: Nature_6_5
data.value: Relax every now and then with a nice, deep breath!

data.name: Nature_6_6
data.value: So, a hasty type like you...

data.name: Nature_7_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the impish type!

data.name: Nature_7_2
data.value: You really like to play a lot! And you enjoy eating a lot!

data.name: Nature_7_3
data.value: You love competition, but you hate losing.

data.name: Nature_7_4
data.value: Your personality seems crystal clear to others. With you, what you see is what you get! You cheer others with your dazzling smile.

data.name: Nature_7_5
data.value: But you may be afraid of showing what's in your heart and revealing your true self.

data.name: Nature_7_6
data.value: You may not want to keep your worries to yourself. You're only human, so ask your friends for advice when you need it.

data.name: Nature_7_7
data.value: So, an impish type like you...

data.name: Nature_8_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the jolly type!

data.name: Nature_8_2
data.value: You have a good sense of humor, and you're compassionate. You're always making others around you laugh.

data.name: Nature_8_3
data.value: You have a sunny, positive outlook, and you have a vitality that raises the lowest spirits to giddy heights!

data.name: Nature_8_4
data.value: Yet, for all your great cheer, you're also open to tears...

data.name: Nature_8_5
data.value: But you bounce between laughter and tears so easily! What an adventure life must be like for you, bouncing around like that all day!

data.name: Nature_8_6
data.value: So, a jolly type like you...

data.name: Nature_9_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the lonely type, at least a little bit!

data.name: Nature_9_2
data.value: You might find that surprising, but do you think it might be a little true?

data.name: Nature_9_3
data.value: You know what they say, though...We're all a bit lonely every now and then!

data.name: Nature_9_4
data.value: You probably keep this fact of life to yourself, though.

data.name: Nature_9_5
data.value: But if there's one thing that brings us all together...it's our need to go it solo!

data.name: Nature_9_6
data.value: So, a lonely and solitary type like you...

data.name: Nature_10_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the naive type! You're so open and innocent!

data.name: Nature_10_2
data.value: What a strong sense of curiosity you have! And you state your opinions purely, sharing exactly what you think.

data.name: Nature_10_3
data.value: You also have an artistic spirit that isn't restrained by social conventions. You startle people with your spontaneity and vision.

data.name: Nature_10_4
data.value: But when you overdo it, other people can have a hard time keeping up with you...

data.name: Nature_10_5
data.value: Have you noticed people looking at you oddly? As if for no apparent reason?

data.name: Nature_10_6
data.value: So, a naive, innocent type like you...

data.name: Nature_11_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the quiet type! And very calm!

data.name: Nature_11_2
data.value: You're great with numbers, and you analyze information before making decisions.

data.name: Nature_11_3
data.value: You rarely make mistakes, because you make decisions so calmly and rationally.

data.name: Nature_11_4
data.value: You also may find it hard to guess what others are thinking, and they may find you a touch cold at times.

data.name: Nature_11_5
data.value: You may not want to keep your feelings to yourself so much of the time.

data.name: Nature_11_6
data.value: So, a quiet and calm type like you...

data.name: Nature_12_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the quirky type!

data.name: Nature_12_2
data.value: You want to be on the cutting edge of fashion! You want to own all the latest stuff, right?

data.name: Nature_12_3
data.value: But you grow bored of your old things and only like new things!

data.name: Nature_12_4
data.value: You're true to your emotions, and you follow your desires.

data.name: Nature_12_5
data.value: People have a hard time keeping up with you because you change so quickly.

data.name: Nature_12_6
data.value: You may want to reflect upon how your words and actions affect others.

data.name: Nature_12_7
data.value: So, a quirky type like you...

data.name: Nature_13_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the rash type, just a little bit hasty at times!

data.name: Nature_13_2
data.value: You may run out of your house and forget to lock the door once in a while. And you may leave things like umbrellas behind when you leave places.

data.name: Nature_13_3
data.value: Maybe you even dash outside in your slippers every now and then!

data.name: Nature_13_4
data.value: Perhaps you even wear your shirts inside out all the time!

data.name: Nature_13_5
data.value: Oh, is that even rasher than you really are? So sorry! But know that your friends think your funny little flubs are adorable!

data.name: Nature_13_6
data.value: So, a rash and hasty type like you... Oh, wait! One more thing!

data.name: Nature_13_7
data.value: You also sometimes reveal your friends' secrets by accidents, don't you! Sorry. Had to be said!

data.name: Nature_13_8
data.value: So, without further ado...a rash and hasty type like you...

data.name: Nature_14_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the relaxed type!

data.name: Nature_14_2
data.value: You're so casual, leisurely, and carefree. You don't rush or stress yourself out, and you don't worry about anything.

data.name: Nature_14_3
data.value: You like to take a seat and kick up your feet! Oh, yes! You definitely have an easygoing personality, and you don't sweat the details.

data.name: Nature_14_4
data.value: People naturally flock to you because they find you to be a free spirit, which is so refreshing!

data.name: Nature_14_5
data.value: So, a relaxed type like you...

data.name: Nature_15_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the sassy type! Or at least somewhat sassy!

data.name: Nature_15_2
data.value: You don't like taking orders. You're a little rebellious and like to disagree.

data.name: Nature_15_3
data.value: You're a lone wolf! You like to keep your distance from groups and go off to do things on your own.

data.name: Nature_15_4
data.value: Older folks may be ones who find you the most disagreeable, even selfish.

data.name: Nature_15_5
data.value: But people younger than you tend to really admire you!

data.name: Nature_15_6
data.value: So, a sassy type like you...

data.name: Nature_16_1
data.value: You seem to be...[pause=0] the timid type. You're quite gentle!

data.name: Nature_16_2
data.value: You're sometimes a little shy about new things, aren't you?

data.name: Nature_16_3
data.value: Do you miss out on some experiences because you get worried about the newness of the challenge?

data.name: Nature_16_4
data.value: Of course, there's also a great benefit in being cautious, isn't there?

data.name: Nature_16_5
data.value: After all, it keeps you nice and safe! You live life at your own speed, with no hurries and no worries!

data.name: Nature_16_6
data.value: So, a timid and gentle type like you...
